Class UserMessage

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class UserMessage extends AbstractMessage
Represents a message originating from the end-user in a conversation. It extends the base AbstractMessage and sets its role to USER.
Author:
anahata-gemini-pro-2.5
